The paper focuses on object detection using deep learning and region proposal methods, which are commonly studied in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The proposed method involves feature extraction and semantic relations, which are also relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper discusses the use of multi-scale proposal layers, which is a common technique in information retrieval (cs.IR) sub-category.
